Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • ProtocolHandler.Transaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Transaction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class Transaction is the fundamental communication element that is passed between Server<->Client, it holds information regarding the request, sender, parameters,data and more.
